{"tid":1827971,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(踢爆)四川辣妹子聯同黨媒做Show","createTime":"2020-01-17T11:31:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T14:14:05.000Z","uid":28970,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"64b696bfc9770c16caebcf2ef3f73b2640fef132","tid":1827971,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:31:29.000Z","msg":"唔知大家仲記唔記得有巴打post過排長龍單野<br />\n<blockquote>市民挺「辣妹」 藍店排長龍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1816907\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1816907</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今日我地黎踢爆做Show!<br />\n原來食環同警蛆一樣用埋曬啲閪招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mNpc5b0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmNpc5b0.png&h=c0911c41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RUThwST.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRUThwST.jpg&h=dc3237ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事後佢一直反反覆覆打比食環 食環一拖再拖！<br />\n我同依位叔叔都識左5、6年 <br />\n佢地就係太貪心先奶野<br />\n大家記得提下屋人上左年紀嘅人唔好咁貪心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22f04d7866674cec8a26d264eff8a32b584b800","tid":1827971,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:33:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4fb7ec9297d4ae6c203a938293cfbbd16c1980","tid":1827971,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:34:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3426aadb087415c95f64805d3f90984ed3b48e01","tid":1827971,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8fe82c9e733293aba90db084d938f73acf96d94","tid":1827971,"uid":21028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"